display_name: SourcingRequestHistory transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 1

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'SourcingRequest_' || "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Workspace_InternalId" AS "SourcingRequest",
    'SourcingRequestHistory_' || "SourcingRequest"."InternalId" AS "ID",
    "SourcingRequest"."InternalId" as "InternalId",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingRequest"."CreateDate") AS "CreateDate",
    "SourcingRequest"."LastModified" as "LastModified",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("SourcingRequest"."TimeCreated" AS TIMESTAMP)) as "TimeCreated",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingRequest"."ContractEffectiveDate") AS "ContractEffectiveDate",
    --"SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin" as "ProjectAddin",                                              JSON FORMAT
    --"SourcingRequest"."ParentDocument" as "ParentDocument",                                              JSON FORMAT
    --"SourcingRequest"."Currency" as "Currency",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "SourcingRequest"."Status" as "Status",
    --"SourcingRequest"."TemplateObject" as "TemplateObject",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "SourcingRequest"."Active" as "Active",
    "SourcingRequest"."NextVersion" as "NextVersion",
    "SourcingRequest"."Description" as "Description",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProcessStatus" as "ProcessStatus",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingRequest"."PlannedStartDate") AS "PlannedStartDate",
    "SourcingRequest"."Changed" as "Changed",
    cast("SourcingRequest"."DocumentVersion" as int) as "DocumentVersion",
    "SourcingRequest"."IsVersionPinned" as "IsVersionPinned",
    "SourcingRequest"."Title" as "Title",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("SourcingRequest"."TimeUpdated" as timestamp)) as "TimeUpdated",
    --"SourcingRequest"."ParentWorkspace" as "ParentWorkspace",                                              JSON FORMAT
    --"SourcingRequest"."BaseLanguage" as "BaseLanguage",                                              JSON FORMAT
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingRequest"."PlannedEndDate") AS "LannedEndDate",
    "SourcingRequest"."Alert" as "Alert",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProcessId" as "ProcessId",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_IsTest" as "ProjectAddinIsTest",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_FollowOnPath" as "ProjectAddinFollowOnPath",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Title_DefaultStringTranslation" as "ProjectAddinPlanTitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_Plan_ProcessId" as "ProjectAddinPlanProcessId",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Workspace_InternalId" as "ProjectAddinPlanWorkspaceInternalId",
    "SourcingRequest"."ProjectAddin_IsSubproject" as "ProjectAddinIsSubproject",
    "SourcingRequest"."ParentDocument_InternalId" as "ParentDocumentInternalId",
    "SourcingRequest"."Currency_UniqueName" as "CurrencyUniqueName",
    "SourcingRequest"."TemplateObject_InternalId" as "TemplateObjectInternalId",
    cast("SourcingRequest"."BaselineSpend_Amount" as float) as "BaselineSpendAmount",
    cast("SourcingRequest"."BaseLanguage_UniqueName" as varchar) as "BaseLanguageUniqueName"
FROM "SourcingRequest"
